  "texts": [
    "In general, it seems that AI can produce results as good as real students and instructors, at least in research studies.",
    "Whether this will be the case in every practical application is another issue.",
    "The goal of peer assessment is to enable formative and/or summative assessment with as much reliability as instructor assessment while developing metacognitive and critical thinking skills in the participants.",
    "It is of course a key question as to whether the introduction of AI enhances these goals."
